                    <span>I'm referring to the audio here.... It's awesome! Just to hear the guy's shrill voice carrying on like that is a huge treat. I was delighted to hear Mr. Hill's stories, told in first person singular, by a man who met commercial giants like Thomas Edison and Henry Ford and the like in person.
<br /></span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">One of the greatest classic books on being rich</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      /
                      <span>4</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-03-19</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book will give you almost everything you need to think and be someone who is rich short of an actually business plan. It works with changing the inner game of wealth with in you. 
<br />
<br />The inner game of "you" is the biggest obstacle that keeps people from having the wealth and life they want. This book does a great job freeing you from the constraints and limitations of your self.
<br />
<br />With one catch. What is your purpose? If you are not fulfilling your purpose you will probably never be wealthy. All you will have is struggle and effort with no real results. When you find what your purpose in life is and make money in a way that helps fulfill your purpose, it will be much easier to be wealthy.
<br />
<br />How do you find your purpose? The simplest way is, what are you most passionate about? What really lights you up and "makes" you happy? That is a huge clue as to what your purpose is. You can also ask your inner knowing, God, your higher self or whatever you want to call "it". Ask it for signs, for clear definitive, there is no doubt signals of what your purpose is. Then watch for those signals. 
<br />
<br />Once you know your purpose apply what you learn in this book and wealth will more than likely follow.
<br />
<br />Don't also fall into the biggest trap of wealth. Many people spend their time and health to get wealth only to then spend all the rest of the time and wealth to get health. A great book to help you easily keep your health as you are building your wealth is The Creator's Manual for Your Body. </span>
                  
              
